snippet.title: SWAP - Official Game Trailer
snippet.description:
SWAP is a simple yet brutally difficult game that will frustrate and personally insult you. Hone your reflexes and steel your emotions to uncover an unexpected story... Or just give up now and save us all some time, the choice is yours.

Game launches on all platforms May 18th 2023!

Steam - Windows / Mac / Linux / Steam Deck
Google Play - Android
Apple App Store - iOS
